'\0',NULL,_binary '\0'),(4,'2026-04-23 22:16:11.000000','2026-04-23 22:17:22.633843','REVIEWS','Reviews that Sample Company customers have left on our products.','entity/GenericTable',_binary '',1,'Reviews',NULL,'PUBLIC','Is it? You tell us!','These reviews aren\'t tied to orders so it is possible people have reviewed products they did not purchase from us.',_binary '\0','database','complete',_binary '\0',NULL,NULL,0,_binary '\0',NULL,NULL,_binary '','unconfigured',NULL,'final',NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary '\0',NULL,_binary '\0'),(5,'2026-04-23 22:16:11.000000','2026-04-23 22:17:22.664344','FEEDBACK','With each order of pies sent out, Piespace includes a place for customers to submit feedback and review their order.','entity/GenericTable',_binary '',1,'Feedback',NULL,'PUBLIC','Is it? WeŌĆÖll let you be the judge of that.','Not every account feels inclined to submit feedback. ThatŌĆÖs cool. ThereŌĆÖs still quite a few responses here.',_binary '\0','database','complete',_binary '\0',NULL,NULL,0,_binary '\0',NULL,NULL,_binary '','unconfigured',NULL,'final',NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary '\0',NULL,_binary '\0'),(6,'2026-04-23 22:16:11.000000','2026-04-23 22:17:22.723626','ACCOUNTS','Information on customer accounts registered with Piespace. Each account represents a new organization signing up for on-demand pies.','entity/UserTable',_binary '',1,'Accounts',NULL,'PUBLIC','Is it? WeŌĆÖll let you be the judge of that.','PiespaceŌĆÖs business operates with a two week trial period. If you see that ŌĆ£Canceled AtŌĆØ is null then that account is still happily paying for their pies.',_binary '\0','database','complete',_binary '\0',NULL,NULL,0,_binary '\0',NULL,NULL,_binary '','unconfigured',NULL,'final',NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary '\0',NULL,_binary '\0'),(7,'2026-04-23 22:16:11.000000','2026-04-23 22:17:22.698783','ANALYTIC_EVENTS','Piespace does some anonymous analytics tracking on how users interact with their platform. TheyŌĆÖve only had time to implement a few events, but you know how it is. Pies come first.','entity/EventTable',_binary '',1,'Analytic Events',NULL,'PUBLIC','Is it? WeŌĆÖll let you be the judge of that.','Piespace has cracked time travel, so keep in mind that some events may have already happened in the future.',_binary '\0','database','complete',_binary '\0',NULL,NULL,0,_binary '\0',NULL,NULL,_binary '','unconfigured',NULL,'final',NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary '\0',NULL,_binary '\0'),(8,'2026-04-23 22:16:11.000000','2026-04-23 22:17:22.544660','INVOICES','Confirmed payments from PiespaceŌĆÖs customers. Most accounts pay for their pie subscription on a monthly basis.','entity/GenericTable',_binary '',1,'Invoices',NULL,'PUBLIC','Is it? WeŌĆÖll let you be the judge of that.','You can group by ŌĆ£Account IDŌĆØ to see all the payments from an account and unveil information like total amount paid to date.',_binary '\0','database','complete',_binary '\0',NULL,NULL,0,_binary '\0',NULL,NULL,_binary '','unconfigured',NULL,'final',NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary '\0',NULL,_binary '\0'),(9,'2026-04-23 22:17:36.995857','2026-04-23 22:17:40.751203','roles',NULL,NULL,_binary '',2,'Roles',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary '\0','database','complete',_binary '\0',NULL,NULL,0,_binary '\0',NULL,NULL,_binary '\0','unconfigured',NULL,'internal',NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary '\0',NULL,_binary '\0'),(10,'2026-04-23 22:17:37.105615','2026-04-23 22:17:40.751203','blacklisted_token',NULL,NULL,_binary '',2,'Blacklisted Token',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary '\0','database','complete',_binary '\0',NULL,NULL,0,_binary '\0',NULL,NULL,_binary '\0','unconfigured',NULL,'internal',NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary '\0',NULL,_binary '\0'),(11,'2026-04-23 22:17:37.181363','2026-04-23 22:17:40.751203','password_reset_token',NULL,NULL,_binary '',2,'Password Reset Token',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary '\0','database','complete',_binary '\0',NULL,NULL,0,_binary '\0',NULL,NULL,_binary '\0','unconfigured',NULL,'internal',NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary '\0',NULL,_binary '\0'),(12,'2026-04-23 22:17:37.227056','2026-04-23 2